{"tid":1463944,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術提議]下次衝不如帶埋國旗去衝","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:09:07.000Z","uid":306694,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cabe23fe723b24c248b77a4492662ced8104f359","tid":1463944,"uid":306694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:06:03.000Z","msg":"班福建佬星期日係北角將國旗當護身符咁用得咁爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，提議下次前線們衝嗰陣都不妨參考下佢地，一黎當護身符，二黎比大陸d媒體影到就可以話比上面d人聽而家香港人唔係要反中同港獨，相反地香港人係熱愛中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（唔好比上面捉住示威者講咩燃起港獨苗頭，公然挑戰國家主權等等去模糊呢場運動既焦點！！），而家係不滿林鄭政府完全無回應過民間訴求，不滿警隊，甚至連成立獨立調查委員會啲咁基本既野都無做！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據特區政府現行的《國旗及國徽條例》第七條：保護國旗、國徽 --<br />\n任何人公開及故意以焚燒、毀損、塗劃、玷污、踐踏等方式侮辱國旗或國徽，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第5級罰款及監禁3年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Duz2xdq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDuz2xdq.png&h=ed7d1439&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n如何正確使用國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好好似佢地咁，調轉左黎影相就唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲星喺左定右都搞唔清仲話愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次出post，唔好插得太勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎指教及各種戰術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cd32a4fb4275f5df7d06ae6548bbef65dcf332","tid":1463944,"uid":306694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329cbbcb16d7ddb478828346f7819556cca5cd76","tid":1463944,"uid":202876,"li